SR:
To reproduce the issue:  
1. Build Tomcat 7.0.0 from SVN r939221.  
2. Use the following code:  

@MySomeAnn  
public class MySomeClass {  
   ...  
}  

@HandlesTypes(MySomeAnn.class)  
public class ModuleInitializer implements ServletContainerInitializer {  
   @Override  
   public void onStartup(Set<Class<?>> classSet, ServletContext ctx) throws ServletException {  
      for (Class<?> targetClass : classSet) {  
         System.out.println(targetClass.getName());  
      }  
   }  
}  

The expected output is 'MySomeClass', but the actual output is 'MySomeAnn'.
